{"article_id":"OyaXq5rvwISgpoF9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Hurricane Irma will `` devastate '' either Florida or neighbouring states ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"the head of the US federal emergency agency has said .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Brock Long said","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"parts of Florida would be without power for days .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Half a million people in the state have been ordered to leave their homes .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Hurricane Irma has left a trail of destruction in the Caribbean ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"affecting an estimated 1.2m people .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"At least 20 people are known to have died so far .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"It has been downgraded to a category four storm ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"but officials warn","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"that it remains `` extremely dangerous '' .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"The US National Weather Service says","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that Irma was expected to bring wind speeds of around 165mph","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"( 270km/h )","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"over the weekend","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"as it hits Florida .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"`` Hurricane Irma continues to be a threat","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that is going to devastate the United States in either Florida or some of the south-eastern states , ''","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Mr Long said .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` The entire south-eastern United States better wake up","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and pay attention , ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"he added .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Florida Governor Rick Scott said","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"all Floridians should be prepared for possible evacuation ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"and issued a stark warning to those in threatened areas .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"`` We are running out of time .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"If you are in an evacuation zone ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"you need to go now , ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"`` Remember ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"we can rebuild your home ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"we ca n't rebuild your life . ''","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"The death toll continued to rise on Friday in the Caribbean .","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"France 's Interior Minister Gérard Collomb said","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"nine people were dead and seven missing in the French territory on St Martin , an island","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"shared with the Netherlands ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"and St Barthélemy ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"known more commonly as St Barts .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Another death","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"- the second -","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"has been confirmed in the Dutch territory of Sint Maarten .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"French officials said","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"six out of 10 homes on Saint-Martin were so badly damaged","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that they were uninhabitable .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"The US Consulate General in Curacao said","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"it believes","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"an estimated 6,000 Americans are stranded on the island .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"French , British and Dutch military authorities have deployed aid","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"- including warships and planes","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"equipped with food , water and troops -","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"to their territories .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Reporting from another badly damaged island , Barbuda ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"the BBC 's Laura Bicker says","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"the destruction there is worse","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"than feared .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"The storm lashed the Turks and Caicos islands","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"and brought torrential rain to the Dominican Republic and Haiti ,","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"before battering the north coast of Cuba and the central Bahamas .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"About 50,000 tourists are fleeing","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"or have fled Cuba ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"with resorts on the north coast now empty ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Reuters reports .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"A huge evacuation of south-eastern , low-lying coastal areas in the Bahamas has been ordered .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"The tourism ministry said in a video statement","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that thousands of tourists left before the storm 's arrival .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Meanwhile Mr Long predicted a `` truly devastating '' impact on Florida .","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"South Florida `` may be uninhabitable for weeks or months ''","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"because of the storm ,","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"the US National Weather Service said .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"On the archipelago of Turks and Caicos , with its population of about 35,000 , one witness described a drop in pressure","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"that could be felt in people 's chests .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Irma ripped off roofs on the capital island , Grand Turk ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"flooded streets ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"snapped utility poles","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"and caused a widespread black-out .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"Governor John Freeman told the BBC","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"that people in low-lying areas were evacuated","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"and sent to shelters .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"The islands ' highest point is only 50m","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"( 163ft ) .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Irma also caused some damage to roofs , flooding and power outages in the northern parts of the Dominican Republic and Haiti .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"widespread damage ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"although extent unclear","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Barbuda :","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"the small island is said to be `` barely habitable '' ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"with 95 % of the buildings damaged .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Antigua and Barbuda Prime Minister Gaston Browne estimates","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"reconstruction will cost $ 100m","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"( £80m ) .","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"One death has been confirmed","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"the small island is said to be `` barely habitable '' ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"with 95 % of the buildings damaged .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"Antigua and Barbuda Prime Minister Gaston Browne estimates","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"reconstruction will cost $ 100m","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"( £80m ) .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"One death has been confirmed","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Anguilla :","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"extensive damage with one person confirmed dead","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"extensive damage with one person confirmed dead","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Puerto Rico :","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"more than 6,000 residents of the US territory are in shelters","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"and many more without power .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"At least three people have died","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"more than 6,000 residents of the US territory are in shelters","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"and many more without power .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"At least three people have died","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"British Virgin Islands :","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"widespread damage reported","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"widespread damage reported","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"US Virgin Islands :","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"damage to infrastructure was said to be widespread ,","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"with four deaths confirmed","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"damage to infrastructure was said to be widespread ,","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"with four deaths confirmed","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"Haiti and the Dominican Republic :","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Both battered by the storm ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"but neither had as much damage","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"as initially feared","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"Irma is due to hit Florida as a category four hurricane on Sunday ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"bringing storm surges and flooding .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"US President Donald Trump said :","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"`` I can say this :","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Florida is as well prepared","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"as you can be","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"for something like this .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"Now it 's just a question of what happens . ''","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"Hurricane and storm surge warnings have been issued for south Florida and the Florida Keys ,","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"the US National Hurricane Center says .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Mr Trump 's own Mar-a-Lago estate in Palm Beach is among those","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"ordered to evacuate ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"the Washington Post tweeted .","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"After ripping through Florida 's Atlantic coast ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"the storm is expected to move into Georgia and South Carolina .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"Georgia Governor Nathan Deal said","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"a mandatory evacuation on the state 's Atlantic coast was scheduled to begin on Saturday .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Roads and airports have been jammed","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"as thousands of people tried to evacuate areas at risk , with reports of fuel shortages and gridlock on some roads .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Many tourists are stranded","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"with no seats left on flights back to their countries","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"as flights to and from airports in Florida are being suspended .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Orlando 's international airport said","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"commercial flights would stop from 17:00 local time","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"( 21:00 GMT )","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"on Saturday .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"Another storm , Jose , further out in the Atlantic behind Irma , is now a category four hurricane , with winds of up to 240km/h","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"( 150mph ) .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"It is following a similar path to Irma","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"and already hampering relief efforts in some of the worst affected areas .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"Residents of Barbuda ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"where 95 % of buildings have been destroyed by Irma ,","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"have now left the island","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"as Jose approaches .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"Hurricane Katia , in the Gulf of Mexico , has strengthened to a category two storm , with winds of up to 140km/h","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"( 85mph ) .","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"A warning is in effect for the coast of the Mexican state of Veracruz","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"and the storm is expected to make landfall on Saturday .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"Please include a contact number","depth":3},{"id":157,"text":"if you are willing to speak to a BBC journalist .","depth":3},{"id":158,"text":"You can also contact us in the following ways :","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":317,"left":314,"right":316,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":314,"left":213,"right":313,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":213,"left":190,"right":212,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":180,"right":189,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":180,"left":163,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":160,"right":162,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":2,"right":161